[normal]&#xa0;[bold]About Keoghs[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Keoghs is the only “top 
[normal]100
[normal]” law firm to focus exclusively on the handling and defence of both mainstream and specialist insurance claims.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] We offer an “end to end” claims service
[normal] to insurers, public sector bodies and self-insured corporate
[normal]s
[normal] which includes pre-litigation, litigation and costs negotiation activities.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] We represent insurers who, between them, provide around 70% of the motor insurance purchased in the 
[normal]UK
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] With almost
[normal] 1,200 dedicated staff Keoghs is a recognised leader in the field.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] In the last 12 months we have been instructed to handle in excess of 35,000 separate matters in total across all classes of personal injury claim.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Keoghs has been closely engaged in the b
[normal]roader Government reforms to the civil litigation system as enacted in Part 2 of the LASPO Act 2012 and other ancillary CPR changes as recommended by Lord Justice Jackson.
[normal]&#xa0;
